    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1941-10-02T14:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1941-10-02T14:00:00-05:00" n="204"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d204">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">800.6363/462: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Chile</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bowers</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Santiago</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-10-02T15:00:00-04:00"
                            >October 2, 1941—3 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 3:41 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>490. My 480, September 28, 11 p.m. The local representative of Standard Oil has
                    been informed that the Government has approved a decree setting up a national
                    oil pool committee in accordance with Department’s proposal and that the decree
                    will be published within the next few days.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bowers</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
